snippet.title: Neofall 2021 Underevent Trailer
snippet.description:
Voice acting by Snowy, Sensational, and the fl studio speech thing
Kyoto art by Wild
Written by ItsKyo
Background music by Snowy
Video Editing by Snowy
Coding by Benathen (ov engine) and WinuX (everything else)
Room in the gameplay by Kikio (tileset by SpiritBlue, and Kikio)

Sensational was supposed to be voicing the event, but he didn't. Sorry the Sensai joke didn't make sense.

Wild: https://gamejolt.com/@AwildBoi
ItsKyo: https://gamejolt.com/@ItsKyo
Snowy :https://soundcloud.com/snowylad
Sensational: https://gamejolt.com/@Sensational
